Features for receptive field finder

controls for a spot:

pause between presentations
in orientation mode:
	go at all orientations or at only 1 orientation
blink mode:
	fixed on duration
contrast
number of cycles to run
move in 100 pixel, 10 pixel, and 1 pixel increments
resize in 10 pixel, 1 pixel increments (both x, y)
show/hide rectangular boundary
rectangle or oval mode
alternate between this spot and alternate spot
mouse interface

spot management:

alternate spot (for comparison)

load/save any of 1000 spot locations (referenced by number)
load into remote computer (maybe control the whole thing from remote computer)

Connecting with the whole thing:

Recenter command for recentering scripts (be careful about screen edge)
Set rect command for scripts

Virtual screen with list of RF's?

